Class SettingsUI

java.lang.Object
com.example.SettingsUI
All Implemented Interfaces:
EventListener, javafx.event.EventHandler<javafx.event.ActionEvent>
public class SettingsUI extends Object implements javafx.event.EventHandler<javafx.event.ActionEvent>
Represents the user interface for the settings menu. Provides sliders for adjusting music and sound effects volumes, and buttons to navigate to the tutorial, parental controls, or main menu. Also includes a close button to exit the settings menu.
